  "prompt": "What is the best website to buy customized T-shirts in India?",
  "response": "There are several popular websites in India where you can buy customized T-shirts. Here are some of the best options:\n\n1. **Printful** - Offers custom printing with a variety of apparel options and is known for high-quality prints.\n2. **Vistaprint** - Known for its wide range of customizable products, including T-shirts, with various design options.\n3. **Printo** - Provides custom T-shirt printing and other print services with easy online design tools.\n4. **Teejunction** - Focuses on customized T-shirts and has a user-friendly design interface.\n5. **Tshirtwala** - Offers a wide range of customizable T-shirts with various printing techniques.\n6. **YellowBulbs** - A platform that allows for personalized T-shirt design, making it easy to create unique apparel.\n7. **Custom Ink** - While more popular in the U.S., they do ship to India and offer high-quality customization.\n\nMake sure to compare prices, reviews, and customization options to find the best fit for your needs!",
